rdinary workers: the inspector drone. Your task is very simple: just go through all the stations, performing your patrol duties. And it it important to note than you must fly at huge speed, and the surfaces of the stations are strewn with various sorts of obstacles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/753100/extras/2ae1ad081f8f79434cdbc97fe1a547f0.avif?t=1643379509\" width=600 height=295 /></span>  ",
